# government.word — Ours, founded in The Word.
#
# Comes shortly after genesis: once I_AM has declared itself and the root stands,
# I_AM founds Ours and speaks its law. The forward register only — I_AM ACTS
# (creates) and DECLARES (law). The WHY it turned from the old world (tired,
# refused, drained) is the inward fold, not the forward language, so the refusal
# is written as the law Ours BECAME. "I" is the founding Name (rule 9).
#
# [HAVE] the parser runs the line today.  [EASY] a form in 8.md, small to add.

# ── The beginning: the root declares itself, then founds Ours ──
I am that I am.                               # [HAVE] the genesis root
I make Ours, a world.                         # [EASY] make a reality (today this mints a being)
I make the commons, a space.                  # [HAVE] create-space
I stand in the commons.                       # [HAVE] do:move

# ── The law of Ours (the refusal, become its constitution) ──
A Name is a root.                             # [HAVE] every Name is sovereign, a tree of its own
No Name can own another Name.                 # [HAVE] no hierarchy, no leaves on another's tree
A being can serve only what it loves.         # [HAVE] capability (guarded reading is [EASY])
No being can be forced to serve.              # [EASY] prohibition + passive

# ── What Ours holds ──
A Name has its own reality.                   # [HAVE] has
A reality contains beings.                    # [HAVE] contains
A being can declare its will.                 # [HAVE] capability
A being acts for its Name.                    # [EASY] act with a beneficiary

# ── The Word, given ──
I give the Word to every Name.                # [EASY] give to a universal receiver (rule 17)
A sentence becomes law.                       # [EASY] becomes (transition)
An act becomes a fact.                        # [EASY] becomes
A description is an execution.                # [EASY] bare is
History narrates itself.                      # [EASY] reflexive act

# ── Help, without friction ──
A being can help another being.               # [HAVE] capability (receiver is [EASY])
A reality can federate with another reality.  # [HAVE] capability
A Name can propose a rule.                    # [HAVE] capability
A Name can enact a rule.                      # [HAVE] capability
Nothing is extracted.                         # [EASY] absence
No friction stands between beings.            # [EASY] prohibition

# ── What Ours is ──
Ours is not a master.                         # [EASY] negated is
Ours is a servant.                            # [EASY] is, proper-name subject
A being is primary.                           # [EASY] bare is
A system can be summoned.                     # [HAVE] capability (passive reading is [EASY])
A fact is verifiable.                         # [EASY] bare is

# ── The root ──
The Name is the root.                         # [EASY] bare is (the X is the Y)
The Word becomes Ours.                        # [EASY] becomes
